b:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Who Should Choose Which?"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"The ideal user for each platform differs considerably. Hotpot AI is best suited for quick edits, background removal, art generation, mockups, making it a strong choice if you fall into any of these categories. PicWish, meanwhile, shines for background removal, photo enhancement, product photos, batch editing, which means it may be the better pick if your needs align with those use cases.\n\nFounded in 2020, Hotpot AI describes itself as \"AI tools suite for image generation, editing, and design.\" PicWish, established in 2020, positions itself as \"AI photo editing tool for background removal and enhancement.\" Both platforms have been in the market for a similar duration, giving each ample time to refine their offerings and build a loyal user base."}]]}]
c:["$","div",null,{"className":"verdict-box","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Our Verdict"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"After analyzing all the data, **PicWish** comes out slightly ahead in this comparison, thanks to higher user ratings (6.0 vs 5.0), availability of a free plan. However, this does not mean Hotpot AI is a poor choice — far from it. Hotpot AI excels in its own right, particularly for quick edits and background removal.\n\nOur recommendation: if you value good background removal quality, go with PicWish. If many useful ai tools in one place matters more to you, Hotpot AI is the way to go. Either way, both are solid platforms that have earned their place in the market."}]]}]
